title: Ajit Pawar, a Veteran Indian Politician, Among 5 Killed in Plane Crash
summary_full: Ajit Pawar, the deputy chief minister of Maharashtra State, was on board a charter jet that crashed as it was coming in to land.
summary_public: Ajit Pawar, the deputy chief minister of Maharashtra State, was on board a charter jet that crashed as it was coming in to land.
